headline: Is General Dynamics (GD) a Safe Haven Among the Best Performing in 2025 Dividend Stocks?
summary: General Dynamics Corporation (NYSE:GD) is included among the 15 Best Performing Dividend Stocks So Far in 2025. General Dynamics Corporation (NYSE:GD) has a strong lineup of defense products, acting as the US government’s main supplier of tanks and heavy land vehicles, while also operating shipyards that build destroyers and nuclear-powered submarines. headline: BAE Systems Supplies BvS10 Armored Vehicle to Sweden, Germany & UK
summary: BAESY's BvS10 rollout begins with deliveries to Sweden, Germany and the UK, launching a 663-vehicle joint procurement deal.
